1003
01:39:12,160 --> 01:39:13,229
So long, Miss Mosey.

1004
01:39:13,480 --> 01:39:14,674
Sorry you're closing the show.

1005
01:39:14,920 --> 01:39:17,309
Nobody wants to come
to shows no more.

1006
01:39:17,800 --> 01:39:21,270
