1029
01:41:09,600 --> 01:41:11,238
lt's the damnedest thing.

1030
01:41:14,320 --> 01:41:18,632
That's the only reason you and l
got into it that time, you know.

1031
01:41:21,280 --> 01:41:22,633
Reckon she likes Dallas?

1032
01:41:23,600 --> 01:41:25,158
Hard to say. Maybe she does.

1033
01:41:28,560 --> 01:41:32,394
