straighted out if l hadn't butted in?

1034
01:41:35,680 --> 01:41:38,240
No, they'd have annulled me too,
even if we had.

1035
01:41:43,440 --> 01:41:45,237
Y'all never even got
into the motel?

1036
01:41:53,600 --> 01:41:55,989
Better get on before we both freeze.

1037
01:42:05,600 --> 01:42:07,238
Here are the keys.

1038
01:42:08,960 --> 01:42:10,359
So long, buddy.

1039
01:42:12,200 --> 01:42:13,269
Be careful.

1040
01:42:14,160 --> 01:42:15,434
l'll take care of the Mercury.

1041
01:42:15,720 --> 01:42:18,075
See you in a year or two
if l don't get shot.

1042
01:44:00,640 --> 01:44:01,629
The sand was blowing.

1043
01:44:01,920 --> 01:44:03,478
l never noticed him.

1044
01:44:03,720 --> 01:44:05,119
Figured nobody'd be
in the street.

1045
01:44:05,400 --> 01:44:07,675
What was he doing out there?

1046
01:44:07,960 --> 01:44:10,679
He weren't doing nothing.
Just a simple minded kid.

1047
01:44:10,920 --> 01:44:12,399
Never had no sense.
Wasn't your fault.

1048
01:44:12,680 --> 01:44:14,398
Hell, no!
l can see that.

1049
01:44:14,680 --> 01:44:16,193
