1050
01:44:16,480 --> 01:44:19,313
Didn't know enough to keep his ass
out of the cold.

1051
01:44:19,560 --> 01:44:21,357
Let's go to the cafe.
Ain't had breakfast.

1052
01:44:21,600 --> 01:44:24,319
l'd like to know what
he was doing with that broom.

1053
01:44:24,600 --> 01:44:27,273
He was sweeping, you sons of bitches!

1054
01:44:27,560 --> 01:44:29,152
