a cup of coffee with you?

1057
01:48:05,320 --> 01:48:06,594
l guess.

1058
01:48:15,160 --> 01:48:17,549
l'm sorry.
l'm still in my bathrobe.

1059
01:48:39,120 --> 01:48:41,236
