without you even here!

1062
01:48:48,560 --> 01:48:51,870
l haven't done anything wrong.
Why can't l quit apologizing?!

1063
01:48:52,160 --> 01:48:53,559
You ought to be sorry!

1064
01:48:54,080 --> 01:48:57,959
