for you. l'd have my clothes on.

1065
01:48:58,240 --> 01:49:01,550
You're the one made me quit caring
if l got dressed or not!

1066
01:49:03,040 --> 01:49:04,871
Just because
your friend got killed...

1067
01:49:05,160 --> 01:49:08,391
