and make it all right.

1068
01:49:08,680 --> 01:49:10,636
l'm not sorry for you.

1069
01:49:10,920 --> 01:49:13,229
You'd have left Billy,
just like you left me.

1070
01:49:13,520 --> 01:49:15,397
l bet you left him plenty of nights...

1071
01:49:15,640 --> 01:49:17,392
...whenever Jacy whistled.

1072
01:49:17,680 --> 01:49:19,398
l wouldn't treat a dog that way.

1073
01:49:19,960 --> 01:49:24,078
You thought l was so old and ugly,
you didn't owe me any explanation.

1074
01:49:24,360 --> 01:49:25,873
You didn't need to be careful of me.

1075
01:49:26,160 --> 01:49:29,197
There was nothing l could do about
you and her, so why be careful?

1076
01:49:29,440 --> 01:49:30,475
You didn't love me.

1077
01:49:31,320 --> 01:49:32,355
Look at me.

1078
01:49:34,320 --> 01:49:35,992
Can't you even look at me?

1079
01:49:48,480 --> 01:49:49,549
See?

1080
01:49:50,960 --> 01:49:52,632
Shouldn't have come here.

1081
01:49:53,280 --> 01:49:55,157
l'm around that corner now.

1082
01:49:56,360 --> 01:49:57,679
You've ruined it.

1083
01:49:58,080 --> 01:50:00,116
lt's lost completely.

1084
01:50:02,600 --> 01:50:05,672
Just your needing me
won't make it come back.

1085
01:51:45,960 --> 01:51:48,030
Never you mind, honey.

1086
01:51:48,880 --> 01:51:50,552
Never you mind.